Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci tu po večierke robíte párty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:46.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade vás musím potrestať.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.73,0:01:49.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Čo to znamená...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, čo sa to deje...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anjel už nie je neškodná?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nie... toto vôbec nie je Kanade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:09.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kým sme neodporovali...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade na nás nikdy nezaútočila.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:16.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:17.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe!  Čo máme robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci, obkľúčte ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.43,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,955.5)}Ha?!  Prečo rozkazuješ {\i1}ty{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.16,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hej! Pusť ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.61,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sústreďte paľbu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musíme to stihnúť, kým použije skreslenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:25.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozumiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:28.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stiahni sa, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Páľte!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je Kanade v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zranili ju dosť vážne, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je rovnaká ako my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dokonca aj smrteľné zranenia sa jej zahoja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako môžu existovať dve rovnaké osoby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:06.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To sa tento svet fakt zbláznil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je tu dôvod.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aký?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:12.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pamätáte na misiu, keď sme sa infiltrovali k Anjelovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V počítači mala softvér na vývoj schopností, však?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bola tam jedna, ktorú sme ešte nikdy nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:24.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musela použiť tú schopnosť.  Harmónia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Harmónia?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je to za schopnosť?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepozeral si na obrazovku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to schopnosť, čo rozdelí jej telo vo dvoje.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Robí si klony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Klon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:41.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tú schopnosť vytvorila sama Anjel pomocou softvéru, áno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale nevyzeralo to, že by bola pod kontrolou...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:47.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá vec bola iná než ona. Viac bojová.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:47.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade používa svoje schopnosti len na ochranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rovnako aj všetky jej čepele.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:53.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boli len proti guľkám.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vážne. Ste absolútne neschopná skupina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san je samozrejme výnimka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo je zložená z debilov.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechaj ma povedať jednu možnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:08.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dôvod, prečo jej klon vybehol, je...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:11.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,že chcela vyvolať silný útok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:14.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako vtedy, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:16.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:20.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správa sa podľa hlavného tela {\i1}odvtedy{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade nikdy predtým nechcela zaútočiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mne je to jedno, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,rozhodne sa jej horlivo zastávaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To pretože...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ľutujem ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nevadí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže, aký problém sme to rozoberali?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.45,0:04:40.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spôsob boja proti klonu Anjela?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si blbý?  Spôsob {\i1}vymazania.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... ak ho vytvorila úmyslene...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.86,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,Čo si to povedal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:46.25,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,Čo robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.25,Dialogue-Alt,,0,0,0,,Pusť ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tak by ho mala byť schopná aj nejako vymazať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:53.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme proste počkať, kým sa zobudí?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:54.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkať.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak by sa dal vypnúť, naozaj by jej urobil toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:01.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pravdepodobne ho vyvolala nevedome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto ho nemohla vymazať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohla sa s ním len biť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, počkaj chvíľu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tá vec nezmizne?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže to tu teraz navždy zostane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz nás nejako nechala odísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale zajtra nás už asi nenechá len tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak prekročíme hranice "ukážkového chovania"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,zmení sa to na krvavú bitku ako včera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj keď už nie je prezidentka študentskej rady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:30.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jej túžba napraviť naše chovanie je stále tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len je trochu útočnejšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:32.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Horšie to už nemohlo byť.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:36.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemáme ani čas sa poriadne zorganizovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžete mi získať trochu času?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako to máme urobiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:46.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choďte do triedy a predstierajte, že dávate pozor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale za žiadnu cenu učiteľa nepočúvajte.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:52.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak začnete brať hodiny vážne, zmiznete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aby vás neobjavil klon Anjela,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,robte nejaké iné veci.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A oddelene sa pokúšte vydržať.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snáď nikto nezmizne.  Dúfam, že sa tu zase stretneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:01.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už dávno {\i}viem{\i0}, že sa rozdelí na dve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chcem vedieť, ako ho mám vymazať.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Angel Player?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je softvérový manuál, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:15.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.  Je celý v angličtine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už takto nemám dosť času.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:18.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!  Zväčšilo sa to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je jej rozsah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je zbytočné.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:27.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:34.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno!  To je ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:38.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak sa mu dá tento príkaz, mal by zmiznúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.92,0:07:41.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, aké sú teda podmienky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Nechápem to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno skúsim ten počítač proste zničiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som blbá?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:53.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potom ten klon nezmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!  Proste to prepíšem do pochopiteľného programu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmizni už!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čakacia doba, 10 sekúnd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:01.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukáž sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čakať 10 sekúnd nejako trvá...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo to nemôžem dať pod 10 sekúnd?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:19.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.  Vyzerá to, že to zafungovalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je ich viac!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vytie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vytvoril to klon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mala by som to zmazať?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie... Zatiaľ som bola veľmi opatrná.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mala by som to meniť čo najmenej...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:40.55,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To by to malo byť fajn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz už len potrebujeme, aby znova použila Harmóniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:47.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Začne Absorbcia a klon sa vráti do jej hlavného tela.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skazili sme to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:56.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno šla niekam von.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To by neurobila.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade sľúbila...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:01.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,že s nami zostane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sľúbila to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Podľa toho neporiadku to vyzerá, že bola unesená.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty!  Čo si urobila?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Ty?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Len som niečo napísala do programu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:18.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak znova použije tú schopnosť, zapne sa schopnosť, čo som pridala,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,klon sa vráti do jej hlavného tela.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To si dokázala?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Skôr som tipovala, ale áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:27.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale nepriateľ zaútočil skôr, ako som čakala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:30.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak skryje hlavné telo, nemôžeme ho zničiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo máme robiť?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:33.05,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Musíme ju nájsť.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počas utekania pred hrozivou Anjelom?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:39.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už predstieranie pozornosti bola pekná otrava...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:41.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako dlho rozptýlenie vydrží?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozptýlením myslíš mňa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:46.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo si sa pridala do GirlDeMo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lebo som obdivovala Iwasawu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:50.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,GirlDeMo majú odvracať pozornosť!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, nie, nie, nie.  Nedokážem odvrátiť pozornosť niekoho tak desivého!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:54.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urob to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:09:56.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto si myslíš, že si?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:59.31,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som tvoj senpai!  To ja mám byť naštvaný!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai, hej?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:02.25,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, tak prepáč!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um.  Asi sa počas koncertu počúram, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urobím, čo môžem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:07.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oceňujem tvoju snahu, ale ešte nemusíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zatiaľ spravme, čo môžeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozkaz pre všetkých členov.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zozbierajte informácie o Anjelovi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.33,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Hey! Yo! Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:18.40,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,It's a moonwalk!  It's a moonwalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.46,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Podľa narýchlo zozbieraných informácií to vyzerá,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:25.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,že je dosť možno držaná v Guilde.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:27.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tom prípade bude v tej novšej.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,V tej, ktorú sme rozbombardovali?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:30.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pasce sú stále funkčné.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Veľmi nebepečné...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:36.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A veľmi ďaleko odtiaľto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase máme ísť tam dole?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minule nás to skoro vyhladilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Čoho sa bojíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:46.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minule si zomrel prvý ty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:49.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Budem pre vás spievať, aj keby som sa počúrala!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ukážem vám, aká som statočná!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:54.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proti tomu taká taktika nezafunguje.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:58.02,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tentokrát žiadne rozptýlenie.  Urobíme to otvorene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počas bojovania s Anjelom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:00.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Presne tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozumiete?  Operáciou je zostúpiť do starej Guildy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:07.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a získať pôvodného Anjela.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Operácia... štart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.44,0:11:28.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že pasce sú ešte vypnuté.  Šťastie~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:32.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... ak sa ukáže Anjel, asi sa aj tak počúram.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale mne to jedno nie je!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je jedno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.58,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale mne to jedno nie je!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:45.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak ju tu rovno máme, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:46.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Páľte!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:51.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:52.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je rýchla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.64,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stále máme ručné zbrane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:56.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obranná schopnosť: Skreslenie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strieľajte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Možno to ukončíme prekvapivo skoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.40,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.03,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa to deje?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:16.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je originál?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.04,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je ďalší klon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo je tu ďalší?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.87,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Každopádne, nepriatelia sa násobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mimochodom, jeho zase dostali prvého, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.  Páľte!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A čo tá za nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na to teraz nie je čas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:33.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najskôr musíme dostať nepriateľa vpredu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:35.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzeráte zaneprázdnene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yurippe, dochádzajú nám náboje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemáme šancu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zoženiem nám východ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:49.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nasledujte ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:50.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ešte 10 sekúnd!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to nestihnete, zostávate tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,10!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:02.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,9!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:03.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,8!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:04.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,7!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,6!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:06.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:07.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:07.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:09.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:10.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,0!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:18.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz sú tu dvaja krutí Anjeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto je ešte horšie ako minulá operácia Zostup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo sú teraz dvaja?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:26.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Klon dokáže používať Sonickú ruku a Skreslenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže nie je prekvapivé, že dokáže používať Harmóniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Úprimne, ste slabomyseľná banda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san je samozrejme výnimka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz vám vysvetlím problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:38.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rob si, čo chceš...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sú tu dva problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zaprvé, koľko klonov bolo vytvotrených?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:46.42,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak klon dokáže vytvoriť klon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:48.67,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,môže ich byť nekonečno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže nie sú len dva?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:54.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mohlo by ich byť desať, dvadsať alebo viac?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj chvíľku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:58.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri tú schopnosť zmenila, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Klony by sa mali vracať do hlavného tela.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:02.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme proste počkať, kým zmiznú?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.93,0:14:05.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je druhý problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:11.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo ak už spravila nejaké kópie predtým, než bola schopnosť zmenená?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:14.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.86,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph.  Sedliaci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Konečne ste si to uvedomili?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:21.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san je samozrejme urodzený šľachtic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:26.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak vedela, že sem pôjdeme...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:28.83,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a začala masovo produkovať klony...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:31.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a rozmiestnila ich okolo Guildy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Potom by...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.67,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.34,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pasca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Už sú za nami dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:39.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nezmiznú.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vy hlupáci nemáte žiadnu šancu na výhru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A vpredu je ich pravdepodobne oveľa viac.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.85,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže nás tu uväznili.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:49.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemôžeme si ani doplniť zbrane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Môžeme len čakať, kým nás dostanú.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:53.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo to vôbec robia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asi si chcú zaistiť úplnú poslušnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.49,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je jej misia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aby sme proste zmizli?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:05.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dokonalý plán, ako nás zabiť jendou ranou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.49,0:15:06.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ideme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase tu je.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Číslo 3, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nemíňaj náboje.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:30.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo plánuješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.65,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsushita piaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choďte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:41.28,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Choďte, kým som ešte pri vedomí!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:44.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prestaň sa snažiť znieť ako hrdina na pokraji smrti!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rýchlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Utekajme, kým máme šancu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.37,0:15:50.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vydrž, Matsushita piaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nechávam to na vás...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nenecháme Matsushitovu-kun obeť prísť nadarmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:02.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vďaka nemu to teraz chápeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.76,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Najlepšie protiopatrenie je spraviť prvý krok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telo Anjela je malé, takže bude najlepšie obmedziť jej pohyb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je jedno, aká silná môže byť,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:14.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,džudo chmat by mal fungovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:18.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lekcie džuda od Matsushity-kun sa budú hodiť.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takže sa vlastne...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,obetuje jeden z nás každému klonovi, ktorého stretneme.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.53,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Správne?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obetovať sa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak zachránime originál...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.54,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,tak zachránime aj ostatných.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.37,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pohnime si.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:35.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Číslo 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.33,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.13,Dialogue-TK,,0,0,0,,Get chance and luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,TK!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:50.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo to tu vyzerá ako v poslednom dieli šónen mangy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zabudni na to.  Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:55.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toto telo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prišiel čas ukázať vám ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.19,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:05.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heh.  Ako keby ma toto vystrašilo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fujimaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:12.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké nerozumné.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:14.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aké nerozumnéééé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:17.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno. Teraz si to uvedomíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si šašo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:23.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pozri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.47,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tam v tmavom kúte.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:27.97,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je tam malé osamelé dievča.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah.  Oh nie, má pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rozosmejem ťa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.44,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si monštrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.48,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-san, to nie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vypočuj ma. Zle som sa vyjadril!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pôjdem ďalší, fajn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.78,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej... povedzte niekto niečo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... Ja ani neviem jeho meno.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:51.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poďme.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:17:58.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Koľká to už je?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:59.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kto vie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.92,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja už to ani nepočítam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraz pôjdem ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:04.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja som na rade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ty vydrž až do konca.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:06.88,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To dievča na teba čaká.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:11.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mám pocit, že čaká.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:14.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Preto musíš pokračovať.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:14.81,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chápeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.69,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A keby náhodou{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:19.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak ideš, tak už choď!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.90,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj na mňa, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miluješ ho, alebo ho nenávidíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.66,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak sme tu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.77,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zvyšky po výbuchu Guildy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pôjdeme na úplné dno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi-kun a Yui pôjdu hľadať originál.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:41.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keď ju nájdete, povedzte jej, nech okamžite použije Harmóniu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:43.50,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Radšej by som mal bojovať ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:46.84,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nepočúval si Hinatu-kun?  To dievča na teba čaká.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.68,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tak budem bojovať ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:50.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si príliš slabá, to nestojí ani za zváženie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.14,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aspoň to zváž!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:53.10,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre, ideme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.89,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Som super-silná!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.23,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že toto je naša posledná operácia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:01.15,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh.  Počkajte na mňa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.07,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to?  Kde je Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.36,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zdalo sa mi, že som počul krátky výkrik...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:12.41,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Padla za obeť Anjelovi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.74,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chúďa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čoskoro ťa zachránime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.91,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zase sme ostali my dvaja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.08,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.18,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rovnako ako minule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.30,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Táto už by mohla byť posledná.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:27.13,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dúfam, že aj je.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:32.71,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej, len tak tu nestoj a pohľadaj originál.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.80,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.27,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ako som si myslela.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.16,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je silná.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zapchaj si uši!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.63,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obranná schopnosť: Vytie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:19.09,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo to sakra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.06,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moje uši!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.20,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neodpadla?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He?  Čože?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.33,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mám zapchaté uši, takže ťa moc nepočujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.38,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No tak, vzdaj sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:52.01,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak chceš, tak ti svojím nožom rozrežem hrdlo.
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.60,0:20:58.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu je!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:21:00.52,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.57,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Si v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:09.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:14.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetci z bojiska položili život, aby sme ťa zachránili.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.24,0:21:15.32,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naozaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.95,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Áno, Kanade.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:20.79,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prepáč, že na teba tlačím, ale musíš použiť jednu schopnosť.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:22.72,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je to Harmónia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to použiješ, všetkých to zachráni.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:27.29,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dobre.  Rozumiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.46,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to použiješ, bude tvoje telo v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:33.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ak to je len raz...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.22,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Obranná schopnosť: Harmónia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.35,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzerá to, že ste zmenili program, čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:46.60,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hej.  Teraz sa všetci vrátia do nej.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.73,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Všetky tie moje bezcitné kópie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.98,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo tým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:54.24,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aj klony majú vlatné vedomie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.70,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A to len tak nezmizne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:57.82,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spoja sa s ňou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:02.99,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kópie, ktoré ste napadli, sa vrátia do jej tela.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.27,0:22:06.00,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A keď prijme všetky tie vedomia naraz...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.21,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nebude to pre ňu ľahké.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:11.75,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Počkaj!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.23,0:22:31.94,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:38.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosím, buď v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.24,0:22:41.45,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:19.62,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo sa nám stane?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.89,0:24:20.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikdy sme Anjela v takom stave nevideli.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:21.51,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ale to bude fungovať len ako dočasné opatrenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:22.59,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Šance sú okolo 1%.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:23.11,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snažíš sa ma vyzliecť?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.91,0:24:22.93,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Čo je toto?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.59,0:24:23.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikto ho trednite!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:23.96,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Viem, že nájdeš pomoc!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:25.56,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nikto aj tak na pomoc nepríde!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.43,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zmiznem?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Na koho strane je asi Boh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.43,0:24:26.39,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vráť sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:27.12,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.12,0:24:29.17,AB Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ja... Všetko si pamätám.
